data.description: This 1,146 square foot 2 bedroom, 2 bath home is sure to impress. Enter the home through the foyer, Bedroom 2 is directly to your left with Bathroom 2 just beyond. Next and to your right is the gorgeous Kitchen Next you enter the expansive living room and dining area that provides a wealth of space and options for the owner to utilize. The living room space is also connected to the large kitchen and breakfast area featuring stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and vinyl plank flooring. Leaving the Livingroom, you will enter the Master Bedroom, showcasing a large, large Walk-in closet, separate shower, tub and double vanity. that affords the owner a spacious place to unwind at the days end. The expansive enclosed patio provides space for entertaining family and friends while keeping them out of the warm summer afternoons and affords the owner a spacious place to unwind at the days end. .
